{
  "title": "ISic000963. I.Sicily inscription 000963",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἄλφιος Κλῶδις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄλφιος\">Ἄλφ(ιος)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλῶδις\">Κλῶδις</span></span> ἐτελεύτησεν πρὸ <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">η</span>´ εἰδ(ῶν) <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Νοβεμ(βρίων) ἡμέρ(ᾳ) Ἡλίου υἱὸς <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\">Λουκίου</span></span> καὶ <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καικειλίας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καικειλίας\">Καικειλίας</span></span> τῶν κειμένων ἰς τὸν πυλ̣[ῶνα] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ἰσερχομένων ἰς δεξιά ἄρξας τὴν δευτέ-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ραν ἀρχὴν καὶ πρεσβίας πρεσβεύσας πρὸς <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>βασιλέα καὶ <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">γ</span>´ παραπονπε͂ς <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ἔζησ(εν) ἔτη λα´ <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡ῆ͡ν͡ε͡ς</span>  <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ι</span>´ ἡ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡έ</span>(ραι) κα´ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἄλφιος Κλῶδις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄλφιος\">ΑΛΦ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλῶδις\">ΚΛΩΔΙΣ</span></span>ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝΠΡΟ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Η</span>ΕΙΔ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΝΟΒΕΜΗΜΕΡΗΛΙΟΥΥΙΟΣ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λουκίου\">ΛΟΥΚΙΟΥ</span></span>ΚΑΙ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καικειλίας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καικειλίας\">ΚΑΙΚΕΙΛΙΑΣ</span></span>ΤΩΝΚΕΙΜΕΝΩΝΙΣΤΟΝΠΥ.[...]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΙΣΕΡΧΟΜΕΝΩΝΙΣΔΕΞΙΑΑΡΞΑΣΤΗΝΔΕΥΤΕ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΡΑΝΑΡΧΗΝΚΑΙΠΡΕΣΒΙΑΣΠΡΕΣΒΕΥΣΑΣΠΡΟΣ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΒΑΣΙΛΕΑΚΑΙ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Γ</span>ΠΑΡΑΠΟΝΠΕΣ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΕΖΗΣΕΤΗΛΑ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Η͡Ν͡Ε͡Σ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ι</span>Η<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Ε</span>ΚΑ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000963_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000963_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000963.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000963-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of IG after Giudica</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>Giudica: KAIKEINAΣ; Giudica: ΠΥΜ.[---]</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"5\">5: <span>Giudica: ΠΡΕΙΒΙΑΣ ΠΡΕΣΒΕΥΤΑΣ</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Franz 1853 5465 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">235</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Cagnat 1906 497 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001116\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001116</a></li><li> Agnello 1953 no.63 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211</a></li><li> Pugliese Carratelli 1956 no.37 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001394</a></li><li> Manganaro 1961 130 n.13 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001447\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001447</a></li><li> Manni Piraino 1973 142-143 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531</a></li><li> Manganaro 1988 36-37 tav.IX.15 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a></li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.490 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\">  Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
